metadata_completo.sinopse:
Pokmon are peculiar creatures with a vast array of different abilities and appearances; many people, known as Pokmon trainers, capture and train them, often with the intent of battling others. Young Satoshi has not only dreamed of becoming a Pokmon trainer but also a "Pokmon Master," and on the arrival of his 10th birthday, he finally has a chance to make that dream a reality. Unfortunately for him, all three Pokmon available to beginning trainers have already been claimed and only Pikachu, a rebellious Electric-type Pokmon, remains. However, this chance encounter would mark the start of a lifelong friendship and an epic adventure!

Setting off on a journey to become the very best, Satoshi and Pikachu travel across beautiful, sprawling regions with their friends Kasumi, a Water-type trainer, and Takeshi, a Rock-type trainer. But danger lurks around every corner. The infamous Team Rocket is always nearby, seeking to steal powerful Pokmon through nefarious schemes. It'll be up to Satoshi and his friends to thwart their efforts as he also strives to earn the eight Pokmon Gym Badges he'll need to challenge the Pokmon League, and eventually claim the title of Pokmon Master. 

[Written by MAL Rewrite]
